title: TSX Clears 33,000 For First Time as Tech Names Rise
description: The S&P/TSX Composite Index surpassed 33,000 for the first time on Thursday. The broad benchmark for Canadian stocks gained 0.3% to close at a record 33,029, powered by gains in tech and industrials shares.
